snippet.title: The greatest and funniest ANIMAL moments #13 - Funny animal compilation - Watch & laugh!
snippet.description:
Animals are so funny, hilarious and cute! They make us smile and laugh and always manage to entertain us! Just look how all these dogs, puppies, cats, kittens, horses, goats, monkeys, geese... behave, play, sleep and snore, fail, make funny sounds, get angry, attack... So funny and cute! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
